'''拉尔夫·S·巴里克'''（{{lang-en|Ralph Steven Baric}}，{{bd|1954年|}}）是一位美国[[病毒学家|病毒学家]]，[[北卡罗来纳大学教堂山分校|北卡罗来纳大学教堂山分校]]微生物学和免疫学院流行病学系[[小威廉·R·凯南|小威廉·R·凯南]]特聘教授，专攻领域为[[冠状病毒|冠状病毒]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Hear from top scientist who has spent 'years' working toward a cure for coronaviruses |url=https://www.msnbc.com/the-beat-with-ari/watch/coronavirus-cure-hear-from-top-scientist-who-spent-years-devising-cure-for-covid-19-80730181693 |website=MSNBC.com |language=en |accessdate=2021-01-21 |archive-date=2021-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114105830/https://www.msnbc.com/the-beat-with-ari/watch/coronavirus-cure-hear-from-top-scientist-who-spent-years-devising-cure-for-covid-19-80730181693 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=For Experts Who Study Coronaviruses, a Grim Vindication |url=https://www.medscape.com/viewarticle/932020 |website=Medscape |accessdate=2021-01-21 |archive-date=2021-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114043000/https://www.medscape.com/viewarticle/932020 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==早年生活==
巴里克成長於[[紐澤西州|紐澤西州]]{{le|卡尼斯波恩特|Carneys Point Township, New Jersey}}，少年時即對生物學感興趣，其母為護理師，巴里克常隨母親待在診間，旁觀醫師與病人的對話。此外他還是一名傑出的游泳選手，獲體育獎學金入讀[[北卡羅來納州立大學|北卡羅來納州立大學]]，主修[[動物學|動物學]]，大學時期巴里克即在一間病毒學實驗室從事研究，1977年畢業後繼續在該校攻讀[[微生物學|微生物學]]博士學位，指導教授為羅伯特·E·約翰斯頓（Robert E. Johnston），1982年博士畢業後至[[南加州大學|南加州大學]]任[[博士後|博士後研究員]]，開始研究[[冠狀病毒|冠狀病毒]]<ref name=newsobserver>{{cite web|url=https://www.newsobserver.com/news/local/education/article242992686.html|title=UNC’s Ralph Baric has long been a leader in virus research. Now, the world is listening|publisher=The News & Observer|author=Kate Murphy|date=2020-05-28|accessdate=2021-01-21|archive-date=2021-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101104730/https://www.newsobserver.com/news/local/education/article242992686.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，指導教授為[[賴明詔|賴明詔]]。1986年，巴里克獲[[北卡罗来纳大学教堂山分校|北卡罗来纳大学教堂山分校]]聘為助理教授，1993年升任副教授，2001年升任正教授<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sph.unc.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/112/2020/04/Baric-SPHCV-Website-04-2020.pdf|title=Curriculum Vitae Ralph S. Baric|publisher=University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill|access-date=2021-07-05|archive-date=2021-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210614203512/https://sph.unc.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/112/2020/04/Baric-SPHCV-Website-04-2020.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==研究==
1990年代巴里克即發表論文，表示冠狀病毒的重組率與[[突變|突變]]率很高，有可能跨越物種障礙感染人類，造成疫情爆發<ref name="BaricFu1995">{{cite journal|last1=Baric|first1=Ralph S.|last2=Fu|first2=Kaisong|last3=Chen|first3=Wan|last4=Yount|first4=Boyd|title=High Recombination and Mutation Rates in Mouse Hepatitis Virus Suggest that Coronaviruses may be Potentially Important Emerging Viruses|volume=380|year=1995|pages=571–576|issn=0065-2598|doi=10.1007/978-1-4615-1899-0_91}}</ref>。2002年他开发出了[[鼠肝炎病毒|鼠肝炎病毒]]（MHV）的反向遗传系统，[[序列組裝|組裝]]MHV的[[互補脫氧核醣核酸|cDNA]]，並以其感染小鼠細胞，此為首次成功組裝[[乙型冠狀病毒屬|乙型冠狀病毒屬]]病毒的完整[[基因組|基因組]]序列<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Yount |first1=B |last2=Denison |first2=MR |last3=Weiss |first3=SR |last4=Baric |first4=RS |title=Systematic assembly of a full-length infectious cDNA of mouse hepatitis virus strain A59. |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-virology_2002-11_76_21/page/11065 |journal=Journal of virology |date=2002-11 |volume=76 |issue=21 |pages=11065-78 |doi=10.1128/jvi.76.21.11065-11078.2002 |pmid=12368349}}</ref><ref name=NYM/>。但當時美國冠狀病毒研究的資金短缺，巴里克的實驗室一度瀕臨關閉。[[SARS事件|SARS事件]]爆發後，他的實驗室經費大幅增加，先後發表多篇有關[[SARS-CoV|SARS-CoV]]與[[MERS|MERS]]病毒機理與治療的研究<ref name=newsobserver/>，尋找可抑制冠狀病毒的藥物<ref name="pmid31924756">{{cite journal| author=Sheahan TP, Sims AC, Leist SR, Schäfer A, Won J, Brown AJ | display-authors=etal| title=Comparative therapeutic efficacy of remdesivir and combination lopinavir, ritonavir, and interferon beta against MERS-CoV. | journal=Nat Commun | year= 2020 | volume= 11 | issue= 1 | pages= 222 | pmid=31924756 | doi=10.1038/s41467-019-13940-6 | pmc=6954302 | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=31924756  }} </ref><ref name="pmid28659436">{{cite journal| author=Sheahan TP, Sims AC, Graham RL, Menachery VD, Gralinski LE, Case JB | display-authors=etal| title=Broad-spectrum antiviral GS-5734 inhibits both epidemic and zoonotic coronaviruses. | journal=Sci Transl Med | year= 2017 | volume= 9 | issue= 396 | pages=  | pmid=28659436 | doi=10.1126/scitranslmed.aal3653 | pmc=5567817 | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=28659436  }} </ref>，並曾試圖開發對抗SARS的[[疫苗|疫苗]]，但未能成功。2006年，巴里克撰文警告合成病毒序列的技術有被用來製作[[大規模殺傷性武器|大規模殺傷性生物武器]]的潛力<ref>{{cite journal|title=Synthetic Viral Genomics: Risks and Benefits for Science and Society|author=Ralph S. Baric|url=https://www.jcvi.org/sites/default/files/assets/projects/synthetic-genomics-options-for-governance/Baric-Synthetic-Viral-Genomics.pdf|year=2006|access-date=2021-01-21|archive-date=2021-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103192435/https://www.jcvi.org/sites/default/files/assets/projects/synthetic-genomics-options-for-governance/Baric-Synthetic-Viral-Genomics.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年，美國政府以可能不慎造成疫情失控為由，公告禁止聯邦政府資助將SARS、MERS或[[流感病毒|流感病毒]]提升毒力、提升傳播能力或擴大宿主物種範圍的{{le|功能獲得型研究|Gain-of-function research}}，巴里克對此深感不滿，寫了一封長信給[[美國國家衛生院|美國國家衛生院]]，表示這項限制會嚴重影響冠狀病毒研究，未來如再有疫情爆發，可能會減慢科學家應變、控制疫情的速度。巴里克當時進行中的研究仍被允許繼續<ref name=NYM>{{cite web|url=https://nymag.com/intelligencer/article/coronavirus-lab-escape-theory.html|title=The Lab-Leak Hypothesis For decades, scientists have been hot-wiring viruses in hopes of preventing a pandemic, not causing one. But what if …?|author=Nicholson Baker|publisher=New York Magazine|date=2021-01-04|accessdate=2021-01-21|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120022351/https://nymag.com/intelligencer/article/coronavirus-lab-escape-theory.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

巴里克與[[中國科學院武漢病毒研究所|中國科學院武漢病毒研究所]]的[[石正麗|石正麗]]合作，製作含有[[SHC014病毒|SHC014病毒]]刺突蛋白、且已適應[[實驗小鼠|小鼠]]體內環境的SARS-CoV重組病毒（SHC014-MA15），發現此病毒可感染人類細胞與小鼠，顯示自然界許多蝙蝠[[嚴重急性呼吸系統綜合症相關冠狀病毒|SARSr-CoV]]可能具有感染人類的潛力<ref name="MenacheryYount2015">{{cite journal|last1=Menachery|first1=Vineet D|last2=Yount|first2=Boyd L|last3=Debbink|first3=Kari|last4=Agnihothram|first4=Sudhakar|last5=Gralinski|first5=Lisa E|last6=Plante|first6=Jessica A|last7=Graham|first7=Rachel L|last8=Scobey|first8=Trevor|last9=Ge|first9=Xing-Yi|last10=Donaldson|first10=Eric F|last11=Randell|first11=Scott H|last12=Lanzavecchia|first12=Antonio|last13=Marasco|first13=Wayne A|last14=Shi|first14=Zhengli-Li|last15=Baric|first15=Ralph S|title=A SARS-like cluster of circulating bat coronaviruses shows potential for human emergence|journal=Nature Medicine|volume=21|issue=12|year=2015|pages=1508–1513|issn=1078-8956|doi=10.1038/nm.3985}}</ref>。此研究於2015年發表，被部分科學家認為風險過大<ref name="Butler2015">{{cite journal|last1=Butler|first1=Declan|title=Engineered bat virus stirs debate over risky research |journal=Nature|year=2015|issn=0028-0836|doi=10.1038/nature.2015.18787}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.the-scientist.com/news-opinion/lab-made-coronavirus-triggers-debate-34502|title=Lab-Made Coronavirus Triggers Debate|date=2015-11-16|author=Jef Akst|publisher={{tsl|en|The Scientist (magazine)|The Scientist}}|accessdate=2021-01-21|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107020056/https://www.the-scientist.com/news-opinion/lab-made-coronavirus-triggers-debate-34502|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年，[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]爆發後，巴里克的實驗室是美國首批獲得樣本進行研究的團隊之一<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.newsobserver.com/news/business/article240892791.html|author=Zachery Eanes|date=2020-03-07|publisher=The News & Observer|title=An air-locked lab at UNC is leading research on cures for the coronavirus|accessdate=2021-01-21|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107020722/https://www.newsobserver.com/news/business/article240892791.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。社交網站上流傳造成疫情的[[SARS-CoV-2|SARS-CoV-2]]為巴里克的實驗室人工製造、再散播於世界各地的[[2019冠状病毒病阴谋论|陰謀論]]，並受到媒體報導，曾在巴里克實驗室工作的卡丽·德宾克（Kari Debbink）甚至收到死亡威脅，多數科學家強烈譴責此類主張SARS-CoV-2非自然起源的陰謀論<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.newsobserver.com/news/local/article241996426.html|title=Debunked COVID-19 conspiracy theory weaves a UNC medical researcher into the tale.|author=Zachery Eanes|date=2020-04-16|publisher=The News & Observer|accessdate=2021-01-21|archive-date=2020-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200416185439/https://www.newsobserver.com/news/local/article241996426.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。巴里克本人則表示自己將專注於工作，並相信絕大多數人都相信他們的研究有助找到對抗[[2019冠状病毒病|2019冠状病毒病]]的療法<ref name=newsobserver/>。

2021年4月，巴里克入選[[美國國家科學院|美國國家科學院]]院士<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nasonline.org/news-and-multimedia/news/2021-nas-election.html|title=News from the National Academy of Sciences|publisher=National Academy of Sciences|date=2021-04-26|access-date=2021-07-05|archive-date=2021-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210923124137/http://www.nasonline.org/news-and-multimedia/news/2021-nas-election.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://sph.unc.edu/sph-news/baric-among-unc-chapel-hill-faculty-named-to-national-academy-of-sciences/|title=Baric among UNC-Chapel Hill faculty named to National Academy of Sciences|date=2021-04-27|publisher=UNC GILLINGS SCHOOL OF GLOBAL PUBLIC HEALTH|access-date=2021-07-05|archive-date=2021-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210812165445/https://sph.unc.edu/sph-news/baric-among-unc-chapel-hill-faculty-named-to-national-academy-of-sciences/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年5月他與其他科學家發表了一封公開信呼籲學界詳細調查SARS-CoV-2的起源<ref name="pmid33986172">{{cite journal| author=Bloom JD, Chan YA, Baric RS, Bjorkman PJ, Cobey S, Deverman BE | display-authors=etal| title=Investigate the origins of COVID-19. | journal=Science | year= 2021 | volume= 372 | issue= 6543 | pages= 694 | pmid=33986172 | doi=10.1126/science.abj0016 | pmc= | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=33986172  }} </ref>。6月巴里克的研究團隊發表論文，以小鼠模型試驗由多種[[SARSr-CoV|SARSr-CoV]]刺突蛋白（SARS-CoV、SARS-CoV-2、[[HKU3病毒|HKU3-1]]與[[SHC014病毒|SHC014]]）的重組mRNA製成之[[RNA疫苗|RNA疫苗]]，發現其有對抗SARS-CoV、SARS-CoV-2（含其變種）、[[WIV1病毒|WIV1]]與SHC014等多種SARSr-CoV病毒株的潛力，可能可作為一對抗SARSr-CoV的廣譜疫苗<ref name="pmid34214046">{{cite journal| author=Martinez DR, Schäfer A, Leist SR, De la Cruz G, West A, Atochina-Vasserman EN | display-authors=etal| title=Chimeric spike mRNA vaccines protect against Sarbecovirus challenge in mice. | journal=Science | year= 2021 | volume=  | issue=  | pages=  | pmid=34214046 | doi=10.1126/science.abi4506 | pmc= | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=34214046  }} </ref>。

==家庭==
巴里克在南加州大學工作期間與妻子托妮·巴里克（Toni Baric）相識，兩人育有四子<ref name=newsobserver/>。

